# Rechecked 2026-04-27:
# schedule VL policy, article URL reverse lookup, monthly UI price metric, rebind
# meta-tests, and local PyInstaller builds do not require new ignore patterns.
# Rechecked 2026-05-03:
# functional hardening, live-smoke JSON logging, `.gitattributes`, core pytest CI subset,
