# already covers generated smoke JSON output, while `.gitattributes` remains tracked.
# Rechecked 2026-05-04:
# implementation-review closure, temporary review-document deletion, PyInstaller build
# output, and expanded fast CI tests are still covered by current build/dist/log/data
# rules. No new ignore patterns are required.
# Rechecked 2026-05-11:
# live-site smoke JSON/stdout/stderr logs, PyInstaller build/dist output,
# SQLite/data files, pytest cache, and Python bytecode from the live-site sample
# refresh and packaged smoke pass are all covered by existing rules. No new
